videos.headline: Walker sinks and-1 bucket for Tennessee
videos.description: Rae Burrell makes a nice bounce pass to Jordan Walker, who is able to sink the basket while drawing a foul.

videos.headline: Davis' contested jumper increases Tennessee's lead
videos.description: Rennia Davis gets the ball and sinks a nice jumper to give Tennessee a bigger lead over South Carolina.
